Packed Services

With our packed service we will manually install WordPress, your WordPress theme and the demo content and will help you to get your website up and running to look exactly like the theme's demo website. In addition, we will setup the theme options and add your logo saving you potentially hours of work!

WordPress Junior

  • WordPress Installation
  • WordPress Theme Integration
  • Setting up like Demo/Preview
  • Page Content Editing
  • Mobile Optimisation
$ 59

WordPress Standard

  • WordPress Installation
  • WordPress Theme Integration
  • Setting up like Demo/Preview
  • 5 Page Content Editing*
  • Mobile Optimisation
$ 139

WordPress Professional

  • WordPress Installation
  • WordPress Theme Integration
  • Setting up like Demo/Preview
  • 10 Page Content Editing*
  • Mobile Optimisation*
